Title: The dark web big three
Book Description: Get and introduction to the big three in censorship-resistant communication- TOR- I2P and freenet and learn how they work and some of the options they have available.

Title: Tor: what is it and is it an onion?
Book Description: A general background of TOR- the onion router. Includes discussion on how to install it and some of the options to create your own dark web sites.
